  <brief_title>Effects of Vibration Training on Exercise Capacity in COPD-patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Vibration Training During a Three-week Rehabilitation on Exercise Capacity in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) III/IV-Patients</official_title>
